ChoiceCondition refer_to_project_root choice_2: [= CurrentBeat beat_1] [= DiscourseAct refer_to_project]
ChoiceCondition refer_to_project_root choice_3: [= CurrentBeat beat_1] [= DiscourseAct refer_to_project]
